cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.IT

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on analyzing the energy consumption of wireless sensor networks.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper deals with controlling and optimizing the energy consumption of the sensor network.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possibility as security measures in WSNs can affect energy consumption.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper may involve analyzing and processing large amounts of data from the sensor network.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as statistical analysis is used to extract effective parameters on energy consumption.
